text: â€¢ GALLERY: The Bulletin's 2nd Annual Fall Foliage Train Rid... Riders traveled on the Providence & Worcester train departing from Norwich on The Bulletin's 2nd Annual Fall Foliage Train Excursion event on Saturday. Passengers rode the train north, along the scenic Shetucket and Quinebaug rivers, through Windham County to Oxford, Mass.
